Input.query:
SELECT t."average_rating", t."title_name_id", p."person_id", n."name"
FROM imdb2."title" as t
INNER JOIN imdb2."person_title" as pt
ON t."title_id" = pt."title_id"
INNER JOIN imdb2."profession" as pr
ON pt."profession_id" = pr."profession_id"
INNER JOIN imdb2."person_profession" as pp
ON pr."profession_id" = pp."profession_id"
INNER JOIN imdb2."person" as p
ON pp."person_id" = p."person_id"
INNER JOIN imdb2."name" as n
ON p."name_id" = n."name_id"
WHERE t."title_id" <= '5441532' OR pt."title_id" BETWEEN '227' AND '322' AND pt."profession_id" = '2' OR p."person_id" < '3546';
